        "created_at": "2024-04-26T00:16:34.935Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Ugh, <em>another</em> Rolland hostile takeover? Ureal, what\u2019s left over there? St Emilion should just secede from France and make Michel the omnipotent sovereign and be done with it. Then St Emilion can be made entirely as a single wine, Chateau Michel or something.</p>",
