        "created_at": "2024-04-26T06:39:34.341Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I had this same <a href=\"http://www.bordeauxwineenthusiasts.com/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=7261\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Larmande</a> a half decade ago.  IIRC the cellarmaster from Soutard had gotten involved?  I don\u2019t think Rolland is consulting here.</p>",
